name: House of warm
description:
Always happy and sad when remember it.

When I was little, my parents always invited me to go to my grandparents' house in the village. I still remember the smell of earth after the rain, I still remember the air mixed with fog, I still remember playing among the dewy grass.

My grandparents' house may be old but very comfortable, as warm as when they give a sense of comfort and love to their grandchildren.

Even though they are now a memory, the affection that was left behind is now a legacy to carry on.
